hlete to win an individual gold medal since 1972.\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 4.3704242372003125e-12, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Co Armagh local, 23, won gold in the 800m freestyle and bronze in the 1500m freestyle.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Daniel pulled out of carrying the Irish flag at Sunday's closing ceremony due to beinghospitalised with a bugbut is now 'feeling better' and eager to see his friends and family back in NI.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 957, \"end\": 959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.656310620904706e-30, \"text\": \"NI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Magheralin Community Association is hosting a 'Welcome Home Event' for the Olympian Gold and Bronze Winner on Tuesday August 13 in St Patrick's Parish Hall from 7pm-8.30pm.\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magheralin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1235810797650227e-23, \"text\": \"Magheralin\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magheralin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Magheralin\"}, {\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1045, \"tit